summary: You might/probably have seen this already, but this is a video from ComicCon in 2015 (I believe) where David Tennant confirms...
question: You might/probably have seen this already, but this is a video from ComicCon in 2015 (I believe) where David Tennant confirms that Rose was a girlfriend. Do with this what you like lol. youtube. com/ watch?v=y2_0auDaNcU
answer:
Oh, you bet I’ve seen it. I was on Tumblr when that happened–and there was great rejoicing.

But I love listening to him say it again.

Her name was Rose. 

And they were together.
